lead_paragraph: Toronto's Marcus Stroman struck out his first batter of spring training during a perfect first inning in the Blue Jays' 5-3 win over the Philadelphia Phillies in the both teams' exhibition opener Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Stroman Starts With a Strikeout, Barney, Blue Jays Top Phils
